Package be.ac.umons.jsonlearning

Class AbstractJSONConformance<A extends net.automatalib.ts.acceptors.DeterministicAcceptorTS<?,​JSONSymbol>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • be.ac.umons.jsonlearning.AbstractJSONConformance<A>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractRandomJSONConformance, JSONPartialEquivalenceOracle, ROCAJSONEquivalenceOracle, VCAJSONEquivalenceOracle, VPDAJSONEquivalenceOracle
    public abstract class AbstractJSONConformance<A extends net.automatalib.ts.acceptors.DeterministicAcceptorTS<?,​JSONSymbol>>
extends Object
    Base class for equivalence checks based on conformance testing of JSON documents.

    In our case, conformance testing means that we generate JSON documents and check that the hypothesis and the classical validator agree on whether the document is valid.
